{"tid":683314,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"UEFA:不會對拉莫斯衝撞龍門事件作出任何行動","createTime":"2018-05-29T15:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T10:05:04.000Z","uid":1121,"like":26,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"81fbafec7053015d3545b7e5a8194b335d386c07","tid":683314,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"Real Madrid's Sergio Ramos to face no action for Loris Karius clash - UEFA<br />\n<br />\nUEFA says it is taking no action against Real Madrid captain Sergio Ramos for a clash with Liverpool goalkeeper Loris Karius in Saturday's Champions League final.<br />\n<br />\nA disciplinary rule which allows cases to be opened for serious misconduct not seen by the match officials &quot;is not applied in this case,&quot; UEFA says.<br />\n<br />\nRamos struck Karius's head with his right elbow in an off-the-ball incident when the score was 0-0 early in the second half of Madrid's 3-1 win on Saturday."},{"pid":"2e2af26178b1aaf00ece3fec93743e7a14742386","tid":683314,"uid":1121,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"Television replays also appeared to show Ramos being pushed toward Karius by Liverpool defender Virgil van Dijk.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;No other protest has been lodged,&quot; UEFA said.<br />\n<br />\nRamos angered fans of Liverpool and Egypt for his earlier challenge that ended Mohamed Salah's game due to an injured left shoulder.<br />\n<br />\nAn online petition demanding UEFA and FIFA take retrospective action against Ramos is nearing 500,000 signatures."},{"pid":"8c93996d655897c7bae0c65d00c1d917f2206766","tid":683314,"uid":1121,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">Television replays also appeared to show Ramos being pushed toward Karius by Liverpool defender Virgil van Dijk.</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;No other protest has been lodged,&quot; UEFA said.<br />\n<br />\nRamos angered fans of Liverpool and Egypt for his earlier challenge that ended Mohamed Salah's game due to an injured left shoulder.<br />\n<br />\nAn online petition demanding UEFA and FIFA take retrospective action against Ramos is nearing 500,000 signatures.</blockquote><br />\n猁鏡：冇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99e3fb4a02d517cf19c185aad3ca4e457eb5db8","tid":683314,"uid":1121,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.steemitimages.com/0x0/https://i.imgflip.com/2b3vz8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.steemitimages.com%2F0x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.imgflip.com%2F2b3vz8.gif&h=f07a9152&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e715af6e1edc6022ad011bc772a43416d727baa","tid":683314,"uid":4646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea39b7d865b66810a5ab4e0127df15462799d30","tid":683314,"uid":66645,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:03:58.000Z","msg":"又少樣野怨....系米想迫死人"},{"pid":"69db43ed968481acb307b5e333518f97e1c90bf0","tid":683314,"uid":65743,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"c99e3fb4a02d517cf19c185aad3ca4e457eb5db8","tid":683314,"uid":1121,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.steemitimages.com/0x0/https://i.imgflip.com/2b3vz8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.steemitimages.com%2F0x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.imgflip.com%2F2b3vz8.gif&h=f07a9152&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:03:58.000Z","msg":"睇睇紅衫4號對手做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile